{"tid":1858948,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"武漢肺炎，大家一定唔可以中招，唔係死既問題","createTime":"2020-02-03T03:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T16:06:17.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1004,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"57b6ee6275f9a6f60a72c1397cb0500395142ec9","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"其實死亡，我知好多人都驚死<br />\n或者因爲各種原因唔可以死，例如照顧父母，照顧仔女，照顧家人，照顧老婆<br />\n<br />\n除左死亡，其實有個更大問題是<br />\n你一中，你就算無死，人生已完，無健康無希望既既感覺<br />\n肺炎既骨枯，肺纖維化，會伴著你人生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n枯骨是一大煎熬，她膝蓋纏着繃帶，半夜經常痛醒，平時不能走遠，也無法久站，走着走着會突然跪下。和朋友出行，一下車就有幾個朋友扶住她，上廁所蹲下後會站不起，亦需要人扶。「不了解的人以為我嬌生慣養。」<br />\n「沙士之後肺纖維化了，很弱，一咳嗽，三個月都好不了。」她說了幾句就會咳嗽，聲音沙啞。以前她很愛唱粵曲，沙士後無力再唱。「拉高音一點就出不到聲音了。」這幾年學了畫畫，她最喜歡畫肖像，尤其是小孩子。「你看多可愛，又有活力。」只是，畫着畫着，偶爾手會不由自主顫抖&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肺纖維化，骨枯<br />\n到時行步路，上斜都辛苦<br />\n比你溝到女神，想屌閪你都唔夠氣同無力<br />\n運動唔洗旨意諗<br />\n行步路都喘氣，行唔郁<br />\n<br />\n人無左健康，比你有錢如bill gate都無意思。以前有個極有錢既油王身患重病，都講過佢寧願自己一無所有，都要健康身體<br />\n健康永遠先於金錢<br />\n<br />\n各位手足要小心唔好中，一中人生就玩完"},{"pid":"29a2919a4954c7883c4fd7998fadf0a6e4165a15","tid":1858948,"uid":23239,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44caf986b2d4d13aea53cfc53e95eab16a845316","tid":1858948,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3253c5305296428c20cb263cb0b8bd2a42100d7","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953a58af290b06059f62348fb43888a5bb7ea071","tid":1858948,"uid":20948,"like":5,"dislike":44,"score":-39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"邊度話會骨枯？纖維化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc70d3c621935d5c87a0b2f8418e85decdf9b39","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca586281c3a4914f0353d1c2f9e57612e1a0a2b4","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":62,"dislike":5,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"953a58af290b06059f62348fb43888a5bb7ea071","tid":1858948,"uid":20948,"like":5,"dislike":44,"score":-39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"邊度話會骨枯？纖維化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"沙士會<br />\n呢種應該跟沙士"},{"pid":"d8602418212dfe97095cce7a16674da5f3d4001f","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"953a58af290b06059f62348fb43888a5bb7ea071","tid":1858948,"uid":20948,"like":5,"dislike":44,"score":-39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"邊度話會骨枯？纖維化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"沙士係呼吸道疾病<br />\n武漢肺炎都係<br />\n應該都係咁"},{"pid":"3171b5b1459a5f840b69fa4b45cc640d3062063b","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"剛度過28歲生日的鄭書棋，10年前在醫療輔助隊（簡稱AMS）服務時，被派到淘大花園護送居民送院檢查，因而「中招」。他憶述，「當時為應付會考，原本已向AMS請假，但淘大花園爆發大型感染，AMS又唔夠人，我恃住後生無有怕便去幫手，負責送感染者家屬去檢驗，數天後便出現呼吸道感染徵狀。」<br />\n<br />\n書棋因為要接受治療，因而錯失考會考。「我住院大半個月，曾因呼吸困難以為死梗。」雖然戰勝沙士，但他出院後晚晚扎醒，數月後證實患上創傷後壓力症，需接受精神科治療。沙士治療的後遺症亦出現他身上，04年他曾難抵關節痛及情緒困擾，一度鬧自殺，幸及時被救回。<br />\n <br />\n　　因為體能不及從前，05年他退出AMS，並到海外進修。10年過去，他相信一切天注定，自稱從事感染病控制工作的他說：「雖然我沒有骨枯，腰股關節卻長期痛，但已學會與後遺症共存，有困難也會從容面對，因為最壞的日子已走過！」<br />\n <br />\n　　現任香港沙士互助會會長的林志釉律師，當年因發燒及咳嗽入院兩日未見好轉，加上肺部有點花，在疑似「中招」下決定接受治療。「當時日日有不少新增感染個案，醫生都建議我接受治療。」"},{"pid":"1347e1bf84c81e2932635797a0690ef6494fbe7a","tid":1858948,"uid":20948,"like":6,"dislike":14,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"d8602418212dfe97095cce7a16674da5f3d4001f","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"953a58af290b06059f62348fb43888a5bb7ea071","tid":1858948,"uid":20948,"like":5,"dislike":44,"score":-39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"邊度話會骨枯？纖維化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"沙士係呼吸道疾病<br />\n武漢肺炎都係<br />\n應該都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"沙士導致骨枯？<br />\n所以呼吸道疾病都係咁？<br />\n應該？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a269d500b75963707e829a7b25a5279d34a5febc","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"疑「中招」 服大量類固醇<br />\n <br />\n　　豈料完成三周類固醇治療，覆診時他發現體內無沙士抗體。講起這無妄之災，他抬頭看著天花板，眼眸泛紅慨嘆，「知道時腦海一片空白&hellip;&hellip;感覺不是嬲，不是無奈，亦不是慶幸，因為我真的入院接受了治療。」<br />\n <br />\n　　治療後首半年，30出頭的他身體明顯轉差，連站也站不穩。「由屋企往地鐵站的百多級樓梯，走一趟要休息幾回。」但最大打擊是病假後即接到大信封。「當年每月供樓要逾萬元，日子有點難捱。」<br />\n <br />\n　　幸好林志釉天性樂觀，失業激發他加快腳步重整生活及另覓工作，07年更自立門戶。但他坦言部分沙士康復者仍揮不去陰霾，談起這段經歷仍有人會抖震飲泣。不過，人總要向前看，他期望所有康復者都能隨歲月過去走出陰霾。<br />\n <br />\n醫護難忘齊心抗疫<br />\n <br />\n　　當年威爾斯醫院有逾238名醫護、職員和病人感染沙士。現任中大校長、當年為該院內科及藥物治療學系部門主管沈祖堯表示，使用類固醇確使沙士病人對病毒產生激烈反應，抗體反致病人出現肺炎，故類固醇應在病毒量降低的後期才使用。"},{"pid":"1a7fe29a7deffa09012a0183f68a1d5c62fc3da1","tid":1858948,"uid":90328,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:04:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nnCoV最恐怖係中左招既話個肺係有不可逆既傷害"},{"pid":"441a239bedcc14b6a739f2f0bc0f1cbe6ec0d5d6","tid":1858948,"uid":280752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"得閒無野做就簽下名啦.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funited-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VwhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=a83894d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general</a>"},{"pid":"efad9a97b8e064e07cd9295287e6cb19f1866a7b","tid":1858948,"uid":110437,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1347e1bf84c81e2932635797a0690ef6494fbe7a","tid":1858948,"uid":20948,"like":6,"dislike":14,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"d8602418212dfe97095cce7a16674da5f3d4001f","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"953a58af290b06059f62348fb43888a5bb7ea071","tid":1858948,"uid":20948,"like":5,"dislike":44,"score":-39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"邊度話會骨枯？纖維化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"沙士係呼吸道疾病<br />\n武漢肺炎都係<br />\n應該都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"沙士導致骨枯？<br />\n所以呼吸道疾病都係咁？<br />\n應該？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"因為食高劑量類固醇"},{"pid":"e153bed35aa84d81022653327ee75ed0e9b4e3bd","tid":1858948,"uid":46042,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府大開中門 送啲病人入嚟俾你地 </span>"},{"pid":"cce44afe0bf01ec0dc08d43aa7c9f18fe71382c5","tid":1858948,"uid":46148,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"骨枯係因為當時使用左劑量大嘅類固醇而出現嘅副作用"},{"pid":"d10beb8951e2b0730f4b198955cf77dd5ee3b8f7","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"香港SARS康復病人　出現嚴重後遺症<br />\n<br />\n去年一場SARS，造成香港至少100多人喪生，不少劫後餘生的SARS病患，抱著感激的心。不過最近卻發現，這些曾經抗煞成功的病人，由於治療時藥物的後遺症，使得他們陸續又出現腰酸背痛等症狀、嚴重者，甚至無法長時間站立！<br />\n凱蒂曾經是一名護士，在SARS肆虐香港的期間不幸遭到感染，雖然花了66天、抗薩成功，挽回一命，他的健康、卻再度亮起紅燈。病人凱蒂：「我出院後開始發覺足踝痛，接下來是膝蓋痛，然後是整個腰都痛"},{"pid":"4c54a3b62345e28611701c878d0150cc3c6ccfe7","tid":1858948,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"凱蒂的症狀稱為「缺血性壞死」，醫生表示，這可能是因為在治療SARS的過程中，一種「皮質類固醇藥」所導致的。醫學證明顯示，這種類固醇藥物會嚴重的傷害骨質，不過當時因為救人第一，香港醫生曾大量使用這種藥，在SARS病患的身上。直到目前為止，所有康復的SARS病人當中，有13%人的都出現類似凱蒂的症狀。"},{"pid":"246c5da9a5c62f275d5e41fdd644e644e2e0e580","tid":1858948,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd010fe58a0d6fd234b1133b5c8595b68e7f759","tid":1858948,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fjSk03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fjSk03.png&h=9fa14800&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af5c2b6ffc84c525fb9ebed47552a22fe1448384","tid":1858948,"uid":345502